<h1>
minify-html
<img width="24" src="https://wilsonl.in/minify-html/icon/cli.png">
<img width="24" src="https://wilsonl.in/minify-html/icon/deno.png">
<img width="24" src="https://wilsonl.in/minify-html/icon/java.png">
